### SavvyBudget API Test Suite (REST Client)
# Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### Register a User
POST http://localhost:8000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

### Login (Obtain JWT Token)
POST http://localhost:8000/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=testpass123
###
### Save access_token from Login response
@access_token = {{response.body.access_token}}


### List Envelopes (Requires Auth)
GET http://localhost:8000/envelopes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Envelope (Requires Auth)
POST http://localhost:8000/envelopes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "description": "Weekly groceries",
  "color": "#38bdf8"
}

### Update Envelope (Requires Auth)
PUT http://localhost:8000/envelopes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Groceries Updated",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "color": "#22d3ee"
}

### Delete Envelope (Requires Auth)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/envelopes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Transactions (Requires Auth)
GET http://localhost:8000/envelopes/1/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Transaction (Requires Auth)
POST http://localhost:8000/envelopes/1/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50,
  "date": "2025-06-22T00:00:00",
  "description": "Grocery shopping"
}

### Delete Transaction (Requires Auth)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/envelopes/1/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
